{"tid":838631,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"Morata交換Lukaku","createTime":"2018-09-27T09:20:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T13:36:39.000Z","uid":197219,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa9be0cd432f5c85c5204bad925d82a4cd8ff2f","tid":838631,"uid":197219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:20:11.000Z","msg":"肯定係winwin<br />\n本來兩隊都分別想要對方球員<br />\n<br />\n獌好多攻勢都由pogba中場分波做<br />\nMorata前場走位較靈活而且配合度高<br />\n前場多變既走動會容易做到空位比中場傳送<br />\n相反Lukaku碌葛咁企係到大而無當<br />\n邊線又冇威脅<br />\n對球隊係負作用<br />\n<br />\n反而車仔戰術上係多用由hazard做突破分波<br />\n咁樣可以騰出空位比lukaku<br />\n以佢既身體優勢係前場做最後一腳<br />\n<br />\n兩個身價相若(而家應該都係)<br />\n另外當年正係摩連奴放棄lukaku, 亦同時係Morata恩師<br />\n<br />\n如果成事一定係winwin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ff4dddb97124afdfd7d24267f328be4f47a0ff5","tid":838631,"uid":5649,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:24:43.000Z","msg":"盧卡古身價一定高過莫達啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9179ebf8606d6fa03ee19670a43512808d37797e","tid":838631,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:28:33.000Z","msg":"上季LKK入16球<br />\n莫拉達入11球<br />\n轉會之前d數據都係lkk大勝"},{"pid":"0a12c8678ed8d52d875252f43482533740aeda94","tid":838631,"uid":161731,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:29:15.000Z","msg":"垃圾換垃圾"},{"pid":"81610f7a7f8793380e9ed77adabda8758781e7a7","tid":838631,"uid":10621,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:30:32.000Z","msg":"點會身價相約<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19448dc7e1cb481bab52b2528f10067cbcc4f5b3","tid":838631,"uid":555,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T09:32:51.000Z","msg":"M達跟摩佬做支點 下下背龍俾人一掂就跌了"},{"pid":"08e25db905849c4827c2dcbe3e90c1ab20e79963","tid":838631,"uid":54025,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":